<p class="">A Jewish home in Palestine.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-78bbd5af-c96d-41e7-a8ed-f77954613264" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
