<p class="">"Shall remain"?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-554e8c8c-f2bb-4ff3-93dd-4d01ae8a9ee3" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
