                Mr. Jones
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-9cb852c1-8818-470d-9465-af44455f9849" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1937-07-21/debates/4e25e9c5-a246-4dac-b679-1a65991f38be/Palestine#contribution-9cb852c1-8818-470d-9465-af44455f9849">
