<p class="">Jaffa is an Arab port.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-b0c9bb26-fe84-4c00-a258-15cc9a6e8690" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
