            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-1d02eed4-6b18-42f4-8b14-4e9fa3ff47bf">
                The Chancellor of the Duchy of Lancaster (Earl Winterton)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-1d02eed4-6b18-42f4-8b14-4e9fa3ff47bf" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
