<p class="">Will the Noble Lord give me an answer to the specific question of whether the Government will consider the transfer of the Mandate to the United States?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-7292ee2d-bdaf-4a2c-9228-f994bb6141de" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
