<p class="">I beg to move, as an Amendment to the proposed Amendment, in line 1, to leave out from the word "proposals" to the end of the proposed Amendment, and to add: <blockquote><q>"contained in Command Paper No. 5513 relating to Palestine should he brought before the League of Nations with a view to enabling His Majesty's Government, after adequate inquiry, to present to Parliament a definite scheme in accordance with the policy as set out in the Command Paper."</q></blockquote> I do not propose to offer any further remarks to the House upon the subject, as I have already been permitted to take part in the earlier part of the Debate.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
